Package view.SetupGame

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    StartGame
    The interface Start game is used in the NewGamePanel and in the LoadGamePanel.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ContinueGamePanel
    The class Continue game panel shows the unfinished games that the user can continue to play.
    CreditsPanel
    The class Credits panel shows the creators of this project.
    DeleteGamePanel
    The class Delete game panel show a list of completed games that can be deleted from the system.
    HowToPanel
    The class How to panel explains the user how to play the game.
    LoadGamePanel
    The class Load game panel shows a list of previous games started by the user, so that they can keep the game configuration and start a new game with it.
    MenuPanel
    The class Menu panel shows the main menu that appears after the login.
    NewGamePanel
    The class New game panel shows the view to create a new game.
    SettingsPanel
    The class Settings panel shows two options for the user to log out and to delete their account from the database.
